<plot>Una Passione Adatta (A Fitting Passion) centres around a shoehorn, a shoe salesman and his customers. The shoe salesman is the 'Shoehorn Gigolo' whose fetish for arousing the sensual side of his customers - by the delicate and stylish use of his shoehorn - is only matched by their ready acceptance of and indulgence in the shoehorn game.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?628496</url></doc>
